{"tid":2427660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民舉「釋放政治犯」橫額 警開咪警告涉煽動分裂國家違《國安法》","createTime":"2021-03-01T03:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T11:40:08.000Z","uid":186,"like":93,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7ac797d05fe1f16517aba7dbe5daf8efd3fb1a","tid":2427660,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"在英華街近隊尾位置，有人拉起「釋放政治犯」橫額，警方隨即警告持橫額人士有機會煽動顛覆國家政權及分裂國家，違反《國安法》，要求他立即收回。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7duWsNH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7duWsNH.png&h=3448e36f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"988a74bcb7eadfce42e34eddec89769a961e31de","tid":2427660,"uid":186,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081135&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3cg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=9b0c99fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081135&h=2a666978\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081135</a>"},{"pid":"586ef14b30470eea88eb68d6d15be9c26f9cc753","tid":2427660,"uid":186,"like":80,"dislike":4,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"市民舉「釋放政治犯」橫額 警開咪警告涉煽動分裂國家違《國安法》<br />\n<br />\n在英華街近隊尾位置，有人拉起「釋放政治犯」橫額，警方隨即警告持橫額人士有機會煽動顛覆國家政權及分裂國家，違反《國安法》，要求他立即收回。<br />\n<br />\n在場的民陣召集人、社民連陳皓桓要求警方解釋「釋放政治犯」如何違反《國安法》，他與警方理論期間，警方開咪警告他破壞社會安寧，要求他立即離開現場。現場人士隨即鼓噪，警方再以限聚令要求現場人士散開。陳邊離開時邊稱：「唔好咁荒謬啦。」"},{"pid":"7e6300145773123696ba9d5980d11b11f6d6d8d3","tid":2427660,"uid":53498,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"586ef14b30470eea88eb68d6d15be9c26f9cc753","tid":2427660,"uid":186,"like":80,"dislike":4,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"市民舉「釋放政治犯」橫額 警開咪警告涉煽動分裂國家違《國安法》<br />\n<br />\n在英華街近隊尾位置，有人拉起「釋放政治犯」橫額，警方隨即警告持橫額人士有機會煽動顛覆國家政權及分裂國家，違反《國安法》，要求他立即收回。<br />\n<br />\n在場的民陣召集人、社民連陳皓桓要求警方解釋「釋放政治犯」如何違反《國安法》，他與警方理論期間，警方開咪警告他破壞社會安寧，要求他立即離開現場。現場人士隨即鼓噪，警方再以限聚令要求現場人士散開。陳邊離開時邊稱：「唔好咁荒謬啦。」"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:17:32.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢都搬出嚟屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f983d3db1a03ad82e9eedb70c10caf4070e8e664","tid":2427660,"uid":38666,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"一呼吸就已經違反國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1033d392b89f278a9245b9d95031203aab366ec0","tid":2427660,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f51a232fabfdea49a8b396303b4dc371a5d1dea3","tid":2427660,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef6d2fd15810ce3254b9b0c67b20bf022149ebab","tid":2427660,"uid":8308,"like":158,"dislike":1,"score":157,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"國安法 + 限聚令 = 萬能<br />\n入唔到國安法就限聚令"},{"pid":"c8e6be2b82bfa32d3ecd0cb18db27a00373b8248","tid":2427660,"uid":55162,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"而家存在已經係犯國安法"},{"pid":"c127182fe44e9735118707bb1c4a05d144a060d1","tid":2427660,"uid":4780,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"即係承認佢地係政治犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4248637494268ebb4fc6321abf7feca182df0a8","tid":2427660,"uid":51271,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:19:44.000Z","msg":"今日割一城，明日割十城就係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>釋放政治犯</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9383f88f4b369953da4e062074dde610beaa4d7f","tid":2427660,"uid":127575,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c8e6be2b82bfa32d3ecd0cb18db27a00373b8248","tid":2427660,"uid":55162,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"而家存在已經係犯國安法